    "name": "Undine",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Undines are humans whose ancestry includes elemental beings of water, such as marids. This connection with the Plane of Water is most noticeably manifested in their coloration, which tends to mimic that of lakes or oceans\u2014all undines have limpid, blue eyes, and their skin and hair can range from pale blue-white to the <br/><br/>deep blue or green of the sea."
        }
    ],
